[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> **Failure Conditions (Game Over):**
[?2004l[?2004h> The game ends permanently in failure when any of these rules are violated:
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> 1. **Overvisit**: Visiting any position more than 2 times (3rd visit)
[?2004l[?2004h> 2. **Premature Finish**: Calling `/finish` when not at the exit
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> **API Usage Examples:**
[?2004l[?2004h> ```bash
[?2004l[?2004h> # Get maze size
